import {
    Box,
    Text,
    Flex,
    Accordion,
    Center,
    Avatar,
    Badge,
    Checkbox,
    Grid
  } from "@mantine/core";
import React from 'react'
import ResponsivePhone from '../ResponsivePhone'

const Index = () => {
  return (
    <Grid mt="xs" pb="xs">
        <Grid.Col span={4}>
        <Accordion.Item value="category-list">
      <Accordion.Control bg="indigo.2">
        <Center>
          <Text fw={700}>Category List</Text>
        </Center>
      </Accordion.Control>
      <Accordion.Panel bg="gray.2">
        <Box
          mb="xs"
          bg="#FFFFFF"
          style={{ cursor: "pointer" }}
          onClick={handleCategoryWithProductClick}
        >
          <Flex
            h={{ base: "auto", md: 100 }}
            justify="center"
            align="center"
            direction={{ base: "column", md: "row" }}
            gap="sm"
          >
            <Flex justify="center" align="center" direction="column">
              <Avatar
                variant="filled"
                radius="sm"
                size="lg"
                color="yellow"
                src="https://blogassets.leverageedu.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/02232228/BSc-Electronics.png"
              />
              <Text size="xs">Electronics</Text>
            </Flex>
            <Flex justify="center" align="center" direction="column">
              <Avatar
                variant="filled"
                radius="sm"
                size="lg"
                color="yellow"
                src="https://hnsfpau.imgix.net/5/images/detailed/240/TH-32JS610Z.01.jpg?fit=fill&bg=0FFF&w=1500&h=844&auto=format,compress"
              />
              <Text size="xs">Accessories</Text>
            </Flex>
            <Flex justify="center" align="center" direction="column">
              <Avatar
                variant="filled"
                radius="sm"
                size="lg"
                color="yellow"
                src="https://i0.wp.com/post.healthline.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Best_Baby_Clothes_1296x728.png?w=1155&h=1528"
              />
              <Text size="xs">Clothing</Text>
            </Flex>
            <Flex justify="center" align="center" direction="column">
              <Avatar
                variant="filled"
                radius="sm"
                size="lg"
                color="yellow"
                src="https://media.gq.com/photos/63eba1b2275d2fef78a425c2/16:9/w_2560%2Cc_limit/nike-running-shoes-streakfly-invincible.jpg"
              />
              <Text size="xs">Shoes</Text>
            </Flex>
            {iconCheckVisible && (
              <Flex h={{ base: "auto", md: `100%` }}>
                <Checkbox defaultChecked />
              </Flex>
            )}
          </Flex>
        </Box>

        <Box
          bg="dark"
          style={{ cursor: "pointer" }}
          onClick={handleCategoryWithProductClick2}
        >
          <Flex
            h={{ base: "auto", md: 100 }}
            justify="center"
            align="center"
            direction={{ base: "column", md: "row" }}
            gap="sm"
          >
            <Flex justify="center" align="center" direction="column">
              <Avatar
                variant="filled"
                radius="sm"
                size="lg"
                color="yellow"
                src="https://blogassets.leverageedu.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/02232228/BSc-Electronics.png"
              />
              <Text size="xs" color="gray.0">
                Electronics
              </Text>
            </Flex>
            <Flex justify="center" align="center" direction="column">
              <Avatar
                variant="filled"
                radius="sm"
                size="lg"
                color="yellow"
                src="https://hnsfpau.imgix.net/5/images/detailed/240/TH-32JS610Z.01.jpg?fit=fill&bg=0FFF&w=1500&h=844&auto=format,compress"
              />
              <Text size="xs" color="gray.0">
                Accessories
              </Text>
            </Flex>
            <Flex justify="center" align="center" direction="column">
              <Avatar
                variant="filled"
                radius="sm"
                size="lg"
                color="yellow"
                src="https://i0.wp.com/post.healthline.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Best_Baby_Clothes_1296x728.png?w=1155&h=1528"
              />
              <Text size="xs" color="gray.0">
                Clothing
              </Text>
            </Flex>
            <Flex justify="center" align="center" direction="column">
              <Avatar
                variant="filled"
                radius="sm"
                size="lg"
                color="yellow"
                src="https://media.gq.com/photos/63eba1b2275d2fef78a425c2/16:9/w_2560%2Cc_limit/nike-running-shoes-streakfly-invincible.jpg"
              />
              <Text size="xs" color="gray.0">
                Shoes
              </Text>
            </Flex>
            {iconCheckVisible2 && (
              <Flex h={{ base: "auto", md: `100%` }}>
                <Checkbox defaultChecked />
              </Flex>
            )}
          </Flex>
        </Box>

        <Box
          bg="dark"
          mt="xs"
          style={{ cursor: "pointer" }}
          onClick={handleCategoryWithProductClick3}
        >
          <Flex h={50} justify="center" align="center" direction="row" gap="sm">
            <Badge size="xs" color="blue">
              All Product
            </Badge>
            <Badge size="xs" color="dark.4">
              Electronics
            </Badge>
            <Badge size="xs" color="dark.4">
              Clothing
            </Badge>
            {iconCheckVisible3 && (
              <Flex h={`100%`}>
                <Checkbox defaultChecked />
              </Flex>
            )}
          </Flex>
        </Box>

        <Box
          bg="#FFFFFF"
          mt="xs"
          style={{ cursor: "pointer" }}
        //   onClick={handleCategoryWithProductClick4}
        >
          <Flex h={50} justify="center" align="center" direction="row" gap="sm">
            <Badge size="xs" color="blue">
              Technology
            </Badge>
            <Badge size="xs" color="dark.4">
              Fashion
            </Badge>
            <Badge size="xs" color="dark.4">
              Sports
            </Badge>
            <Badge size="xs" color="dark.4">
              Home
            </Badge>
            {iconCheckVisible4 && (
              <Flex h={`100%`}>
                <Checkbox defaultChecked />
              </Flex>
            )}
          </Flex>
        </Box>
      </Accordion.Panel>
    </Accordion.Item>
        </Grid.Col>
        <Grid.Col span={4}><ResponsivePhone /></Grid.Col>
        <Grid.Col span={4}>3</Grid.Col>
    </Grid>
  )
}

export default Index
